Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.50,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：「後藤洛克」音同「進行登記」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:14.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最…最初就設定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是要進行登記吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.30,kakushigoto text - 2,,0,0,0,,是後藤洛克吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤洛克…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我覺得很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  我交表了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:30.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,決定了嗎  名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,名字最初就設定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.02,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1E1F23&\frz326.5\pos(982.4,393.6)}狗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:35.02,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\frz323.6\pos(761.6,742.4)}洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:38.02,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H3D3C4D&\pos(819.2,748.8)}命名  後藤洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤洛克…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,洛克  洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,區政府的人真是取了個好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在我聽到的瞬間就覺得「就是這個了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以嗎  不是自己取的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好名字的話  跟是誰取的沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是呢  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤洛克  進行登記…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.28,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很喜歡這類呢  筧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是會想著用初始設定命名狗狗什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很有小姬的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是我的初始設定就是個可愛的名字就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:43.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在日本  比起姓氏後半的名字改起來更困難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:49.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  對小羅砂來說「羅砂」這個名字已經深入腦海了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在再改為其他的名字會很有違和感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最初接受的印象挺難改的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:59.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎  我很有「羅砂」的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:00.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是肯定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管kobu平有沒有變為正藏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直不都是kobu平的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:05.95,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：指日本落語家林家正藏  因不滿以身材被命名的藝名「kobu平」  後自行改為「正藏」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:11.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我大概能理解到為啥他會讓身邊的人抓狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起最初的印象很重要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:25.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,線稿的線總是無法超越草稿的線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:28.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個  漫畫家經常提起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便如此也得幹下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行  果然沒辦法超越草稿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等…您在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就把草稿原封不動的登載上去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:47.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.15,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\c&H3C3F4C&\pos(1336,324.8)}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.36,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\c&H3C3F4C&\pos(1614.4,329.6)}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:48.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.15,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\c&H3C3F4C&\pos(862.4,187.2)}是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.36,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\c&H3C3F4C&\pos(1136,195.2)}是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等…等等？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把草稿原封不動的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒能注意到這麼簡單的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:58.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在印刷技術發達的今天  完全可行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:03.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把創作者最好的產物登上紙面正是責編的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去讓還停留在昭和時代的編輯部管理層大吃一驚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是革命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,據我所知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能被允許用草稿登載的在這業界只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.98,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：指富堅義博
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就是第二人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒能被允許
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:27.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個狗和少女的畫像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還沒送回倉庫麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下次芥子來的時候我會給他說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,算了  我自己放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「最初的印象就是全部」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「那個印象是改不了的」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:54.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也許身在匆忙的社會之中  大家都沒什麼閒餘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,放這塊就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那傢伙畫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:24.54,kakushigoto in 12,,0,0,0,,{\frz335\pos(841.6,273.6)\fad(0,1000)}平凡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:24.54,kakushigoto in 12,,0,0,0,,{\frz336.2\pos(760,508.8)\fad(0,1000)}未來預想圖（暫定）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,無論做再多的人生規劃  最後還是各種妥協
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是就是  最初的願景果然超越不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:43.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會超越的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最初的願景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:47.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,會超越的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和姬一起  越過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不能越過去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不可能超越得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,超越草稿的線  我畫不出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打…打擾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:25.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她叫相賀加代
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想看狗狗一直等著的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:31.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以  趕快把洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:35.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,洛克  看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:39.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對了  我去倒點果汁過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:45.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:46.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我被小姬拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:52.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,關於什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:58.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是前陣子轉校過來的  但最初搞砸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:03.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在自我介紹的時候太緊張了在人前一句話都說不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自己築起了高牆  變成誰都無法接近的氛圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:13.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正當我認為一生都要以這種角色度過的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「我開始養狗了」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:21.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有小姬這樣的救世主在  我感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:25.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定人生還能重來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下…下次來看看我家的狗狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:34.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人生的救世主麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讓姬來拯救我是怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以呢  能畫出超越草稿的線了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:57.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想到了個秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要畫出超越草稿的線稿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只要降低草稿的水平就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您是天才麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:16.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,路上走好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,建校紀念日放假哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好想跟姬出去玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,去不就好了  畢竟是自由職業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「難道是什麼高度自由可以隨時放假的工作麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被這樣推測很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是建校紀念日每年都有必要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:46.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在五周年十周年之類的關鍵點慶祝下倒是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師  今年要加油了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都已經十一月了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:57.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  周刊少年漫畫人十一月的三號刊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,將會迎來創刊第38周年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:03.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又是不上不下的地方呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全不在節骨眼上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這閃亮的周年紀念日的年份裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,編輯部將會團結一致高歌猛進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打起幹勁雖然是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不能等到40周年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.36,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord3\fad(0,500)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1E1F23&\pos(841.6,123.2)}周刊少年漫畫人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.36,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord3\fad(0,500)\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1E1F23&\pos(897.6,854.4)\frz7.613\frx10\fry356}祝  用愛和勇氣  38周年!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管是雜誌還是其他的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:23.36,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\fad(500,500)\bord2\frz340.3\pos(337.6,659.2)}2萬4000下載量達成紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在不上不下的地方慶祝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:26.12,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fad(500,0)\frz17.63\pos(606.4,153.6)\c&H373744&}創業27周年  特別售賣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:26.12,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs45\fad(500,0)\c&H373744&\frz289.1\pos(1372.8,356.8)}廣告品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定是某種危險訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.62,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz332.3\pos(1040,587.2)}遺憾紀念組
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.62,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自新澤基榮漫畫「3年奇面組」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:33.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全變回平時的十丸院了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:36.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是想說說周年紀念日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什麼周年紀念日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,紀念日女子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比起這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:43.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是這樣的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:51.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣的  是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為你看啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:55.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如此如此這般這般…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:57.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:02.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這期周刊風之緊身褲迎來了連載第100回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們居然完全沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一點慶祝的話都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,100回  那又怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,100回會有什麼事情發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十丸院君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:23.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想100回也意味著我對這雜誌做出了一定貢獻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:27.18,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs50\frz336.7\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H1E1F23&\move(654.4,336,668.2,-114.8,23,4069)}感謝支持  連載100回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是不是應該爭取個封面或者彩頁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又或是搞點贈品企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:31.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少也得給我寫幾句話宣傳一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:35.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您事先不給我說  我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這種事情  責編不計數的話就沒人能注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可是注意到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我又不是初代責編
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能計數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再說了  100回又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您也是紀念日女子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.49,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:55.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您要使用職權欺壓我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你才是在道德綁架我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:03.05,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:06.38,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喘氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:09.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說起來  羅砂小姐你要是知道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:10.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就說一聲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:13.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.93,0:13:16.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想給你們個驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,驚喜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想給你們個驚喜慶祝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.03,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H617879&\3c&HBBD5D3&\frz30.89\move(-24,696,118,702,0,401)}祝賀第100回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.32,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H617879&\3c&HBBD5D3&\frz30.89\pos(182.4,331.2)}祝賀第100回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.32,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs45\c&H617879&\3c&HBBD5D3&\frz259.4\pos(884.8,820.8)}恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:26.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡  我畫了快閃族的路人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有沒有很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:31.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以…以後別做像這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您又是這樣啦  明明開心得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實我是因為太過突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以根本不敢插話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,檢查的時候沒有一個人注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:47.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟到最後大家都很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:56.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡…歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了  看上去慌慌張張的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:04.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,隱瞞事情可不怎麼…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.32,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}刺疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:08.70,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}刺疼  刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這句話如迴旋鏢一般刺進了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我真的沒什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實您也不好說她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:23.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬也到了有心事的年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:30.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真可愛  究竟有著什麼心事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢  看上去像紙片一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:35.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,應該是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,班上男孩子送給她的情書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:43.77,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看反應應該是嚇著了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬也是現如今的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,之後也會創個共同賬號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:52.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,發個「馬上就交往一周年了」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.91,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7C7B7B&\pos(142.4,424)\b1}榮❤姬  CP垢一周年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.91,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：CP垢指的是一對情侶共同使用一個賬號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.91,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H878689&\pos(844.8,723.2)}祝交往一周年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.91,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H878689&\pos(948.8,811.2)}這之後也會恩愛下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:52.91,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\c&H878689&\pos(184,950.4)}高中生CP  身高差20cm  共同賬號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:58.54,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}共同賬號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.54,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fad(650,0)\c&H3B3B48&\pos(896,761.6)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:07.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個  我還是拒絕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是情書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:13.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:20.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸的意見的話  還是拒絕的好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:22.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去向她表明拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:25.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:28.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要不要爸爸跟著你去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟他選擇了你  想來應該是個有品位的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可要不失禮貌  真誠地向人拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不用了  我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:38.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:44.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,敢對我女兒出手的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,讓我看看是怎麼一個臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  關於答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:57.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.94,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord3\frz306.3\pos(484.8,148.8)\c&HA051D6&}時間：星期六  中午12點後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.94,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord3\frz306.3\c&HA051D6&\pos(219.2,355.2)}地點：愛優家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.94,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord3\c&HA051D6&\frz225.3\pos(1172.8,315.2)}小姬  這週六請務必來參加我的生日聚會！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,邀請函？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是哦  你以為是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒…沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼拒絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:19.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,10歲或者100回的生日  替對方慶祝的話對方也會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:20.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,100回？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且爸爸你也說拒絕比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:30.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我其實也想替她慶祝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  如果我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:36.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就得招待她們來我的生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,叫她們來不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們家不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:44.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只有爸爸你一個人準備太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:51.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,裝飾  蛋糕  還有炸雞  都得準備很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:53.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像這種事情  該慶祝的時候就要慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:04.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說不定以後想要慶祝也無法慶祝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,別人為你慶祝的時候欣然接受就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:14.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以  明年姬的生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你把你的朋友們都叫來  我們熱熱鬧鬧舉辦一場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:20.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎  裝飾這些東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸會精心裝飾屋子的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:23.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:26.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸會準備一個大到你們可以爬上去的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,炸雞也要很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:30.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸會炸到多得你們吃不完的炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:37.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸會鍛鍊廚藝做出好吃到你們吃不下了還是想吃完的炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以…去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:46.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟她準備東西總是很周到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,應該會留下寫有慶祝聚會的步驟之類的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:50.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和姬的比起來  給我準備的就很草率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:54.21,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(910.4,769.6)\c&H3A3A3A&\frz352.9}30-39歲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.72,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz353.6\pos(825.6,462.4)}慶祝聚會手冊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,找到了  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我多去汐越老師那裡幾趟吧  一定要學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可要好好替朋友慶祝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.53,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCDFFFF&\frz358.1\pos(785.6,284.8)}BBC  廚房教室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:27.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,根據本部的方針  我們不招收單身男性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:32.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為以搭訕為目的男性總是絡繹不絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:36.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然  我知道後藤先生不是那種人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  真讓人頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:43.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個 作為代替您覺得這樣如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的生日聚會你們會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我爸爸會炸很多炸雞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:51.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次聽說姬的生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:55.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我絕對會去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:05.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對的對的  做得很好  後藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  生日聚會玩的開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:23.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這位是爸爸的料理指導老師  運動會也來了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好久不見  小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,將火調至微火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:31.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生日聚會過得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:40.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特別開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們家也不能輸給她們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明年  叫上你的朋友們  熱熱鬧鬧舉辦一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯  我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:54.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是和爸爸兩個人的生日聚會我也很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:57.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢  那種當然是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:03.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和朋友過的生日聚會還有和爸爸兩個人過的生日聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定每年都要過兩次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有洛克  那就是三個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:17.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但要是過兩次生日的話  我不就長兩歲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那樣的話就會馬上長成大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:26.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那樣也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:27.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.79,0:20:41.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這裡也和中目黑的家裡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:46.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,唯一的區別就是這裡能夠看見大海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想起來了  這間房子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這間房子本來是我和爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:15.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一家三口居住的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:21.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,實際上在這裡畫也太勉強了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.63,0:21:24.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想也算不上勉強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:27.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是我倒不太喜歡來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:28.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是這麼一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:35.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟要忙周刊連載還得自己一個人撫養孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:37.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的很艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:39.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他其實一直都很想隱居的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:46.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在鄉下的話他的工作會很顯眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:51.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,或許他是對那個鎌倉的家留有懷戀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.74,0:21:56.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以才在中目黑建了一間構造相同的房子吧
